                  porta quam, vitae gravida dui augue at dui. Nunc mauris velit,
                  tempus sit amet congue ut, aliquet a eros. In in sapien eget
                  lectus tempor tristique at sed dolor. Nullam pharetra nulla
                  risus, in dapibus lectus feugiat quis. Maecenas egestas
                  egestas sapien quis sodales. Aenean sagi
                </p>
              </div>
              <p className="text-muted fw-light fs-7">
                <BsClockFill size={12} className="me-1" />
                10th June 2021 5:14 pm
              </p>
            </Col>
          </Row>
        </Container>
      </Collapse>
    </Container>

















              );
            })}
          </Col>
          <Col
            sm={3}
            md={3}
            lg={3}
            className="d-none d-md-block d-lg-block d-xl-block"
          >
            <Sidebar />
          </Col>
        </Row>
      </Container>
      <ScrollToTop />
    </div>
  );
}

export default Home;
